I"ô<p>getting started with IRC</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://weechat.org/files/doc/stable/weechat_quickstart.en.html">WeeChat Documentation</a></li>
  <li>[Getting started Youtube video on WeeChat]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SEAne0vihac)</li>
</ul>

<p>install weechat</p>
<pre><code class="language-console">sudo yum install weechat
</code></pre>

<p>First add an IRC server</p>
<pre><code class="language-console">/server add freenode chat.freenode.net
</code></pre>

<p>Connect to IRC server you just added</p>
<pre><code class="language-console">/connect freenode
</code></pre>

<p>Search for channels whose name contains <code>python</code></p>
<pre><code class="language-console">/msg alis list *python*
</code></pre>

<p>Search for channels whose topic contains <code>python</code></p>
<pre><code class="language-console">/msg alis list * -topic *python*
</code></pre>

<p>Commands: <a href="https://gist.github.com/xero/2d6e4b061b4ecbeb9f99">https://gist.github.com/xero/2d6e4b061b4ecbeb9f99</a></p>
